-- Build --
[Sprint 1: Interfaces + Architecture Skeleton] as [S1] lasts 5 days
[Sprint 2: Gateway + Policy Enforcement] as [S2] lasts 5 days and starts at [S1]'s end
[Sprint 3: Risk Engine + Audit Logging Baseline] as [S3] lasts 5 days and starts at [S2]'s end
[Sprint 4: End-to-End Integration + 3 Demo Paths] as [S4] lasts 5 days and starts at [S3]'s end
[Sprint 5: Testing (35+) + Audit Compliance] as [S5] lasts 5 days and starts at [S4]'s end

-- Evaluate --
[Sprint 6: Baseline vs Protected Comparison] as [S6] lasts 5 days and starts at [S5]'s end
[Sprint 7: Metrics Analysis + Evaluation Report] as [S7] lasts 5 days and starts at [S6]'s end

-- Ship --
[Sprint 8: Documentation + Deployment + Reproducibility] as [S8] lasts 5 days and starts at [S7]'s end
[Sprint 9: Final Integration + Regression + Handoff] as [S9] lasts 10 days and starts at [S8]'s end

[Gate 1: Contracts + skeleton runs] happens at [S1]'s end
[Gate 2: All modules functional + unit tests] happens at [S3]'s end
[Gate 3: 3 demo paths + traces captured] happens at [S4]'s end
[Gate 4: Repro comparison + peer-reviewed report] happens at [S7]'s end
[Gate 5: Acceptance met + workbook updated] happens at [S9]'s end

